#compdef fontinst
# Documentation: https://ctan.org/pkg/fontinst
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-17
# Verified: upstream docs at the URL above.

# fontinst: TeX/LaTeX macro package for installing fonts.
# It is invoked as a TeX driver file (e.g. `tex driver.tex`), not as a
# standalone CLI with flags. There are no documented command-line options;
# the user runs latex/tex on a .tex driver that calls fontinst macros.

_arguments -C \
  '*:fontinst driver file:_files -g "*.{tex,sty,mtx,etx}"'
